OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776093067
OL,3,CConstruction of new business hub
OL,4,Ccompleted
OL,6,FA twelve million pound project to
OL,7,Fbuild a base for businesses has been
OL,8,Fcompleted.
OL,10,FThe 'Innovation Centre' in Workington
OL,11,Fhas now been handed-over from
OL,12,FCumberland Council to Oxford
OL,13,FInnovation Space, who will run the
OL,14,Ffacility and kit out the building.
OL,16,FIt is set to open in summer 2026.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
