CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776093067
OL,3,CConstruction of new business hub
OL,4,Ccompleted
OL,6,FSituated on the former Central Car
OL,7,FPark in the town centre, it was funded
OL,8,Fby central government as part of the
OL,9,F#23.1 million Workington Town Deal
OL,10,Fproject.
OL,12,FThe centre is designed to provide
OL,13,Fpurpose-built accommodation for
OL,14,Fentrepreneurial businesses, and bring
OL,15,Fmodern office space to Workington.
OL,17,FStart-up businesses and "ambitious
OL,18,Fsmall businesses with clear growth
OL,19,Fpotential" are the target tenants of
OL,20,Fthe centre.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776093067
OL,3,CConstruction of new business hub
OL,4,Ccompleted
OL,6,FIt is hoped the centre will compliment
OL,7,Fthe 'Digital Accelerator Hub' at Lakes
OL,8,FCollege, another project from the
OL,9,FWorkington Town Deal. This hub aims to
OL,10,Fdevelop digital expertise and skills
OL,11,Fin the local population.
OL,13,FThe Innovation Centre also has a focus
OL,14,Fon digital technology and
OL,15,Fmanufacturing, to support the region's
OL,16,Fcurrent and future economic needs.
OL,18,FOxford Innovation Space experts will
OL,19,Faid in helping businesses achieve
OL,20,Ftheir ambitions and sustainably scale.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
