PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776093067
OL,3,CConstruction of new business hub
OL,4,Ccompleted
OL,6,FDuring the building's construction,
OL,7,Fapprentices took part in 211 weeks
OL,8,Fworth of work, while three T-level
OL,9,Fstudents took part in 1-day-a-week
OL,10,Fwork placements.
OL,12,FJo Stevens, Managing Director of
OL,13,FOxford Innovation Space, added: "We
OL,14,Fare delighted to be working in
OL,15,Fpartnership with Cumberland Council to
OL,16,Fbring the Workington Innovation Centre
OL,17,Fto life.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
