CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1776093067
OL,3,CConstruction of new business hub
OL,4,Ccompleted
OL,6,F"Our focus will be on creating a
OL,7,Fvibrant, supportive environment for
OL,8,Fdigital technology and advanced
OL,9,FmanufacturingJbusinesses with real
OL,10,Fambition to grow."
OL,12,FLeader of Cumberland Council, Cllr
OL,13,FMark Fryer, said: "This is a new and
OL,14,Fexciting project that is going to
OL,15,Fbenefit the entire Cumberland
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
